{
 "name": "RPlog_Much_Too_Frightened_to_Tease_a_Padawan",
 "title": "Much Too Frightened to Tease a Padawan",
 "summary": "Seeking respite from the Basilica and the news of battle, the Jedi Ai'kani Za'netra wanders into the lightless depths of Coruscant's Abyssal Ruins, drawn by a message delivered through a hobbling old woman. There the unbalanced Twi'lek Tyy'sun, hidden in the dark, taunts her with mocking proclamations and stages a confrontation, sending youths to rob her of her credits and robes at blasterpoint. Ai'kani calmly turns aside their fumbling attack, controlling one boy's arm rather than harming him and absorbing a blow rather than injure the young. Tyy'sun reveals himself to gloat over her, and Ai'kani, pained but unbroken, makes her way back out of the ruins toward the light above.",
